<headline>Special Weather Statement issued January 12 at 5:19PM EST  by NWS Pittsburgh</headline>
<description>...MIXED PRECIPITATION AND BRIEF HEAVY SNOW POSSIBLE THIS EVENING FOR
MERCER...LAWRENCE...BUTLER...ARMSTRONG...INDIANA COUNTIES...
Snow will briefly mix with rain and sleet this evening. Briefly
high snowfall rates are possible. This could lead to isolated
slippery road conditions and a quick inch of accumulation.
Conditions can deteriorate rapidly in winter weather situations. Be
prepared for snow covered roads and reduced visibilities. Slow
down and allow extra time when traveling.</description>
